{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"iddb2e95a9-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s325"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"325"},"text":"§ 325.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Examinations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"As a condition of membership such banks shall likewise be subject to examinations made by direction of the Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System or of the Federal reserve bank by examiners selected or approved by the Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"iddb2e95aa-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1913-12-23/ch6/s9"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1913, ch. 6, § 9","children":[],"tail":" (par.), as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1917-06-21/ch32/s3"},"text":"June 21, 1917, ch. 32, § 3","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/40/233"},"text":"40 Stat. 233","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1935-08-23/ch614"},"text":"Aug. 23, 1935, ch. 614","children":[],"tail":", title II, § 203(a), "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/49/704"},"text":"49 Stat. 704","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"iddb2e95ab-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"iddb2e95ac-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"iddb2e95ad-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section is comprised of the seventh par. of section 9 of act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1913-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1913","children":[],"tail":", as amended. The seventh par. constituted the fifth par. of section 9 in 1917 ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/40/232"},"text":"40 Stat. 232","children":[],"tail":"), became the sixth par. in 1927 ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/44/1229"},"text":"44 Stat. 1229","children":[],"tail":"), and became the seventh par. in 1950 ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/64/458"},"text":"64 Stat. 458","children":[],"tail":"). For further details, see Codification note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s321"},"text":"section 321 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"iddb2e95ae-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"changeOfName","id":"iddb2e95af-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Change of Name","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 203(a) of act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1935-08-23"},"text":"Aug. 23, 1935","children":[],"tail":", changed name of Federal Reserve Board to Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
